                   ├─ thread_crisis    ──→ conflict       │
                   ├─ location_flashpoint ──→ encounter   │
                   ├─ faction_instability ──→ political   │
                   ├─ thread_mystery   ──→ investigation  │
                   └─ thread_diplomatic ──→ negotiation   │
```

